query:
SELECT c.accountId, a.id as adAccountId, a.accountName, a.marketplace, COUNT(*) as campaignCount 
FROM campaigns c 
LEFT JOIN ad_accounts a ON c.accountId = a.id 
GROUP BY c.accountId, a.id, a.accountName, a.marketplace;
